title: Julian Daduica’s DSCI 521 Website
text:
Welcome to My Portfolio
Welcome to my personal website! Here you’ll find details about my projects and experience in data science.
Hello, my name is Julian Daduica. I was born in Coquitlam, BC and moved to Prince George when I was 8 years old. I continued through high school and univeristy at the University of Northern British Columbia. I have a BSc in Biochemsitry and Molecular Biology. I also did some reseach on Forrest microbial communities using various bioinformatic techniques.
I am currently 23 years old and attending the Univeristy of British Columbia Master of Data Science program. I enjoy playing soccer, running, and skiing.
